# FRETSTORM environment variables
#
# The MVP is a 100% static front-end and needs NO env vars to run or deploy.
# These are placeholders for the (roadmap-only) "search & source" pipeline
# described in ROADMAP.md — Feature 3 is intentionally NOT built into the MVP.
#
# If/when you implement the pluggable AudioSource backend as Vercel serverless
# functions, set these in the Vercel dashboard (Project → Settings → Environment
# Variables) — never commit real keys.

# Example: metadata search provider (e.g. for song lookup by name)
# AUDIO_SEARCH_PROVIDER=
# AUDIO_SEARCH_API_KEY=

# Example: licensed audio/preview provider
# AUDIO_PROVIDER_BASE_URL=
# AUDIO_PROVIDER_TOKEN=
